{"name": "starlette-async-jinja", "metadata": {"name": "starlette-async-jinja", "version": "1.8.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Framework :: AsyncIO", "Framework :: FastAPI", "License :: OSI Approved :: BSD License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP :: Dynamic Content", "Typing :: Typed"], "home_page": null, "license": "BSD-3-Clause", "documentation_url": "https://github.com/lesleslie/starlette-async-jinja", "dependencies": ["starlette", "jinja2", "jinja2-async-environment"], "summary": null, "upload_time": 1735532466}, "documentation": ["# starlette-async-jinja\n\n[![Code style: crackerjack](https://img.shields.io/badge/code%20style-crackerjack-000042)](https://github.com/lesleslie/crackerjack)\n\n### Jinja2 is_async template support for Starlette +\n\n## About\n\n- Provides AsyncJinja2Templates class which enables use of the is_async Jinja environment flag with\nStartlette and Starlette based applications like FastAPI\n- Integrated [Jinja Partials](https://github.com/mikeckennedy/jinja_partials)\n  and [Jinja Fragments](https://github.com/sponsfreixes/jinja2-fragments)\n- Supports asynchronous template loaders (examples [here](https://github.com/lesleslie/jinja2-async-environment/blob/main/jinja2_async_environment/loaders.py))\n\n## Issues\n\n- Only [asynchronous template loaders](https://github.com/lesleslie/jinja2-async-environment/blob/main/jinja2_async_environment/loaders.py)\n  (not yet tested but should work) are currently supported\n\n- The Jinja bytecodecache requires an asynchronous Redis backend\n\n## Usage\n\nImport AsyncJinja2Templates:\n```python\nfrom starlette_async_jinja import AsyncJinja2Templates\n```\n\nReplace Jinja2Templates with AsyncJinja2Templates:\n```python\ntemplates = AsyncJinja2Templates(directory='templates')\n```\n\nRender the async template in the response:\n```python\nasync def homepage(request: Request):\n    return await templates.TemplateResponse(request, 'index.html')\n```\n\nor:\n```python\nasync def homepage(request: Request):\n    return await templates.render_template(request, 'index.html')\n```\n\n\n## Acknowledgements\n\n\n## License\n\nBSD-3-Clause\n"], "modules": [{"name": "starlette_async_jinja", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "starlette_async_jinja.AsyncJinja2Templates", "xref": {"fqname": "starlette_async_jinja.responses.AsyncJinja2Templates", "project": null}}, {"name": "starlette_async_jinja.BlockNotFoundError", "xref": {"fqname": "starlette_async_jinja.responses.BlockNotFoundError", "project": null}}, {"name": "starlette_async_jinja.JsonResponse", "xref": {"fqname": "starlette_async_jinja.responses.JsonResponse", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "starlette_async_jinja.responses", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "starlette_async_jinja.responses.JsonResponse", "bases": ["JSONResponse"], "methods": [{"name": "starlette_async_jinja.responses.JsonResponse.render", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "content", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "t.Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "starlette_async_jinja.responses.BlockNotFoundError", "bases": ["Exception"], "methods": [{"name": "starlette_async_jinja.responses.BlockNotFoundError.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "block_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "template_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname":